# DriveShare — Android Native (Kotlin + Jetpack Compose)

App per motociclisti: tracking GPS in background, waypoint con foto/note, import/export GPX, gestione garage moto.

## Architettura

```
com.driveshare.app/
├── data/
│   ├── local/
│   │   ├── dao/          ← Room DAOs (6: Route, TrackPoint, Waypoint, Motorcycle, Expiration, Maintenance)
│   │   ├── entity/       ← Room Entities (6 tabelle)
│   │   └── DriveShareDatabase.kt
│   ├── gpx/
│   │   └── GpxManager.kt ← Parser GPX (import) + Exporter GPX (export) + Haversine
│   ├── model/
│   │   └── Models.kt     ← Domain models (GeoPoint, TrackingState, RiderStats, etc.)
│   └── repository/
│       ├── RouteRepository.kt   ← Routes + TrackPoints + Waypoints + Stats
│       └── GarageRepository.kt  ← Motorcycle + Expirations + Maintenances
├── di/
│   └── DatabaseModule.kt ← Hilt DI: Room DB + DAOs
├── service/
│   └── TrackingService.kt ← ⭐ Foreground Service: FusedLocationProvider, notification, state emission
├── ui/
│   ├── theme/            ← Material3 theme (Red600 primary, dark mode support)
│   ├── navigation/       ← Screen sealed class + NavHost
│   ├── components/       ← StatCard, OsmMapView (osmdroid wrapper)
│   └── screens/
│       ├── dashboard/    ← Stats overview, quick actions, upcoming expirations
│       ├── tracking/     ← ⭐ Live tracking UI, start/pause/stop, waypoint dialog, Google Maps launch
│       ├── routes/       ← Route list, GPX import, delete
│       ├── routedetail/  ← Map + stats + waypoints + GPX export/share
│       ├── garage/       ← Motorcycle, expirations, maintenances
│       └── settings/     ← GPS interval, min distance, screen on, units
├── util/
│   └── Utils.kt          ← GeoUtils (haversine), FormatUtils (date, duration, distance, speed, currency)
├── DriveShareApp.kt      ← Hilt Application, osmdroid config, notification channels
└── MainActivity.kt       ← Scaffold + BottomNav + NavHost
```

## Stack Tecnologico

| Layer | Tecnologia |
|-------|-----------|
| UI | Jetpack Compose + Material3 |
| Navigation | Navigation Compose |
| State | StateFlow + ViewModel |
| DI | Hilt |
| Database | Room (SQLite) |
| Location | FusedLocationProviderClient (Play Services) |
| Maps | osmdroid (OpenStreetMap — no API key) |
| Images | Coil |
| Permissions | Accompanist Permissions |
| GPX | Custom XML parser (XmlPullParser) |
| Background | Foreground Service (location type) |
| Serialization | Kotlin Serialization |

## Come funziona il Tracking

1. L'utente preme "Avvia Tracking" → viene avviato un `Foreground Service` con notifica persistente
2. Il service usa `FusedLocationProviderClient` con alta accuratezza (3s interval, 5m min distance)
3. Ogni posizione viene salvata come `TrackPointEntity` nel Room DB
4. Lo stato viene emesso via `StateFlow` statico (`TrackingService.trackingState`)
5. L'utente può mettere in pausa, aggiungere waypoint con note/foto, aprire Google Maps
6. A fine giro, il percorso viene salvato con stats aggregate (distanza, durata, velocità)

## Flusso principale del rider

```
Dashboard → Avvia Tracking → [App va in background] → Rider usa Google Maps
→ Si ferma → Torna sull'app → Aggiunge foto/nota al waypoint
→ Riprende il giro → Fine → Salva percorso → Dettaglio con mappa e stats
→ Esporta GPX / Condividi via share intent
```

## Database Schema

```sql
routes (id, title, description, distance_km, duration_seconds, avg_speed_kmh, max_speed_kmh, ...)
track_points (id, route_id FK, latitude, longitude, altitude, speed, accuracy, bearing, timestamp, point_index)
waypoints (id, route_id FK, latitude, longitude, title, note, photo_path, type, timestamp, sort_order)
motorcycles (id, name, brand, model, year, license_plate, photo_path, total_km)
expirations (id, motorcycle_id FK, type, expiration_date, notes, reminder_days_before)
maintenances (id, motorcycle_id FK, type, date, km_at_service, cost, notes, next_due_date, next_due_km)
```

